2013-10-09 - Version 0.1.2

Summary:
Some bugfixes.

Bugfixes:
- Quote extra configure arguments for nginx to passenger module call.

2013-10-09 - Version 0.1.1

Summary:

This release introduces custom installation of nginx using passenger. This would be useful if you wish to have additional nginx modules. The new class parameters for this are $nginx_source_dir and $nginx_extra_configure_flags. See README.markdown for additional details.

Bugfixes:
- Converts old puppet code to 3.0

